file_content.text: I knew it would come down to one last stand. Face me!
Let's try a whole new paradigm!
You want chaos? Blood and metal? If you live long enough, the Vigilant will give them to you.
I haven't lost. Not yet. Not while the Vigilant... still....
Here's a little something from our friends on Corellia.
Feisty, aren't you? Bringing contingencies online!
And you thought you could face the Vigilant? Ha!
You don't have time to lie there and bleed.
Only the toughest make it to the top of the ladder!
All the forgotten tech of the galaxy--re-forged, perfected in Czerka's hands!
Vigilant! Stand with me! Agh, I'll stop them myself!
Without Czerka, this galaxy would be nothing!
Tatooine was a misstep! But oh, what we've learned since then--
